LICENCE
=======

The following restrictions apply to the preview version of Gamma Patrol
(referenced as the GAME below):

1.) You can download, install and use the GAME free of charge.

2.) If you redistribute the GAME (placing it on a CDROM, a webpage, a FTP 
    server or any other medium), you have to use an unmodified package as
    it is available in the download page of the GAME's website (look at
    README for the exact URL).

3.) You are NOT allowed to distribute modified versions of the GAME.

4.) You are NOT allowed to distribute parts of the GAME (graphics, sounds,
    music or any other part of the GAME), or use parts of it in another
    product.

5.) You are allowed to distribute screenshots of the GAME for the purpose
    of reviews, articles etc.

6.) And finally (when there is a final version): if you like the game, I 
    would appreciate, if you register for the final version.

